{"type":"message","id":"12346af1","parentId":"3a6c6d5e","timestamp":"2026-03-13T01:17:36.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"图片文件都在。但是之前飞书上传一直报错\"params error\"，可能是因为图片太大（有些超过 1MB）。让我先试试上传小一点的文件，或者用 base64 方式上传。\n\n另外，飞书多维表格的附件字段需要通过特定的方式关联。我需要：\n1. 先上传图片到飞书云空间\n2. 获取文件的 file_token\n3. 在表格记录中使用附件字段，格式是 [{\"file_token\": \"xxx\"}]\n\n让我先尝试上传一张小图片试试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_84ca8f9286d246dd942d7a63","name":"feishu_drive_file","arguments":{"action":"upload","file_path":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/bili_images/bili_BV15QAUzXEtP_7.png","name":"bili_7_Mad-Monk.png"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773364651179}}
