{"type":"message","id":"b0bd6164","parentId":"b0b44489","timestamp":"2026-03-13T01:37:42.628Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户需要在线访问 HTML 报告，我需要总结几种部署方案并询问用户选择哪个方案来帮他实现。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哥哥，我给你整理了**4 个在线部署方案**，文件已保存到：\n\n```\n/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/部署指南.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 快速推荐\n\n### 最简单 → Netlify Drop（30 秒）\n1. 打开 https://app.netlify.com/drop\n2. 把 `bili_images` 文件夹拖进去\n3. 获得链接：`https://xxx.netlify.app/B 站评论图片报告.html`\n\n### 最稳定 → GitHub Pages（永久）\n需要 GitHub 账号，我可以帮你写自动化脚本\n\n### 国内最快 → 阿里云 OSS（约 3 元/月）\n适合国内团队访问\n\n---\n\n## 💡 我的建议\n\n**先用 Netlify Drop 测试**，确认效果后再用 GitHub Pages 长期托管。\n\n哥哥你选哪个？我帮你写自动化脚本 🏹"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773365857874}}
{"type":"message","id":"009332fd","parentId":"b0bd6164","timestamp":"2026-03-13T01:38:35.177Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-13 09:38:34 GMT+8] Feishu[hunter] DM | 用户154215 (ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3) [msg:om_x100b5402e76d3130c3b7a5d70957ded]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5402e76d3130c3b7a5d70957ded\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3\",\n  \"sender\": \"用户154215\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-13 09:38 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"用户154215 (ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3\",\n  \"name\": \"用户154215\"\n}\n```\n\n谷歌文档能实现吗 我有谷歌账号"}],"timestamp":1773365915167}}
{"type":"message","id":"153c9b6d","parentId":"009332fd","timestamp":"2026-03-13T01:38:59.233Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问能不能用谷歌文档实现在线访问，他有谷歌账号。这个方案确实可行，但我需要用 Python 脚本调用 Google Docs API 来创建文档并插入图片。不过 Google API 需要 OAuth 认证和 API 密钥配置，比较复杂。\n\n更简单的方式是：\n1. 用 Google Drive 上传 HTML 文件并分享\n2. 或者用 Google Sites\n3. 或者创建一个 Google Doc，插入图片和文字\n\n但问题是 Google API 需要配置认证，比较麻烦。最简单的方案其实是：\n1. GitHub Pages（免费，需要 GitHub 账号）\n2. Netlify Drop（免费，拖拽上传）\n3. Google Drive 分享 HTML 文件\n\n让我给用户一个实用的方案，用 Google Drive 分享 HTML 文件，或者用 Google Sites 创建页面。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可以的哥哥！用谷歌账号有更简单的方案 🏹\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 谷歌方案对比\n\n### 方案 1：Google Drive 托管 HTML（最简单 ⭐⭐⭐）\n**优点**：无需配置、拖拽上传、立即分享  \n**缺点**：预览功能有限\n\n### 方案 2：Google Sites（推荐 ⭐⭐）\n**优点**：可视化编辑、免费托管、自定义域名  \n**缺点**：需要手动创建页面\n\n### 方案 3：Blogger（免费博客）\n**优点**：谷歌官方、免费、稳定  \n**缺点**：适合长文，不太适合报告\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 我帮你实现方案 1（Google Drive）\n\n让我先帮你准备一个**优化版的 HTML 文件**（使用图片 URL 而不是本地路径），然后你上传到 Google Drive 就能在线访问了：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0c9512490e5943f29715088a","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nB 站评论图片 - 生成在线版 HTML 报告\n使用图片 URL，可上传到任何平台在线访问\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport time\n\n# 配置\nBV_ID = \"BV15QAUzXEtP\"\nOUTPUT_DIR = \"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/bili_images\"\n\n# 评论数据（使用 B 站原图 URL）\ncomments = [\n    {\"user\": \"鲍比烤迪克\", \"comment\": \"有没有大佬帮忙翻译翻译是因为啥 [笑哭]\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/e307257281cc97cb9a43ce67b209e23a603268895.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"队友脚下火\", \"comment\": \"之前可以正常玩，昨天突然出现这样的报错\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/3da0984bb0a1744a77510231bbe215e4518548367.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"參悟自由的意義\", \"comment\": \"嘗試，還是這樣\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/d63b678c314176e678d6fb6c8a18156814110469.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"起语风\", \"comment\": \"有没有大佬知道这个怎么解决\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/8dbd37793a7a714ab1a3d3abcd7798d9358323258.png\"},\n    {\"user\": \"赤瞳的夜刃\", \"comment\": \"这又是什么问题报错，在线等很急\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/54bfa81769c32f2591c9a86177e4067a302272043.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"阿拉斯苒\", \"comment\": \"这个是什么情况\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/73c2c27e1c9737325ca53a19af83d0e314681573.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"Mad-Monk\", \"comment\": \"按照 up 的指南从头到尾试了一遍，依然如此，游戏时长 50 分钟，满满的解密环节，可能跟我用的是网吧的电脑\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/e73288fb9697e7f6e8d863b8fc33931b554905270.png\"},\n]\n\n# 生成 HTML\nhtml = f\"\"\"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>B 站评论图片抓取 - {BV_ID}</title>\n    <style>\n        * {{ margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }}\n        body {{\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }}\n        .container {{ max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }}\n        h1 {{\n            text-align: center;\n            color: white;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }}\n        .subtitle {{\n            text-align: center;\n            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }}\n        .card {{\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }}\n        .card:hover {{\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }}\n        .card-header {{\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 25px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }}\n        .user-name {{ font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: 600; }}\n        .comment-index {{\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\n            padding: 5px 15px;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }}\n        .card-body {{ padding: 25px; }}\n        .comment-text {{\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;\n        }}\n        .image-container {{ text-align: center; }}\n        .image-container img {{\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }}\n        .image-container img:hover {{ transform: scale(1.02); }}\n        .image-info {{\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            color: #666;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }}\n        .footer {{\n            text-align: center;\n            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }}\n        .stats {{\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }}\n        .stat-item {{\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }}\n        .stat-number {{ font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; color: white; }}\n        .stat-label {{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 0.9em; }}\n        .btn {{\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease;\n        }}\n        .btn:hover {{ transform: scale(1.05); }}\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>📸 B 站评论图片抓取</h1>\n        <p class=\"subtitle\">BV 号：{BV_ID} | 生化危机 9 Crash 崩溃报错</p>\n        \n        <div class=\"stats\">\n            <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                <div class=\"stat-number\">{len(comments)}</div>\n                <div class=\"stat-label\">条评论</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                <div class=\"stat-number\">{len(comments)}</div>\n                <div class=\"stat-label\">张图片</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                <div class=\"stat-number\">100%</div>\n                <div class=\"stat-label\">原图画质</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\"\"\"\n\nfor i, c in enumerate(comments, 1):\n    html += f\"\"\"\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <div class=\"card-header\">\n                <span class=\"user-name\">@{c[\"user\"]}</span>\n                <span class=\"comment-index\">评论 #{i}</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card-body\">\n                <div class=\"comment-text\">\n                    {c[\"comment\"]}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-container\">\n                    <img src=\"{c[\"url\"]}\" alt=\"{c[\"user\"]} 的评论图片\" onclick=\"window.open('{c[\"url\"]}')\">\n                    <div class=\"image-info\">\n                        🔗 <a href=\"{c[\"url\"]}\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn\">查看原图</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\"\"\"\n\nhtml += f\"\"\"\n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <p>🏹 小猎 · 信息捕手 | 生成时间：{time.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")}</p>\n            <p>💡 点击图片可以全屏查看 | 数据来源于 B 站评论区</p>\n            <p style=\"margin-top:15px;font-size:0.85em;opacity:0.7;\">\n                📥 <a href=\"https://github.com/your-username/bili-comments\" style=\"color:white;\">获取源码</a>\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n\"\"\"\n\n# 保存 HTML\noutput_file = os.path.join(OUTPUT_DIR, \"B 站评论图片报告 - 在线版.html\")\nwith open(output_file, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n    f.write(html)\n\nprint(f\"✅ 在线版 HTML 报告已生成：{output_file}\")\nprint(f\"\\n📤 上传到 Google Drive 步骤：\")\nprint(f\"   1. 打开 https://drive.google.com\")\nprint(f\"   2. 上传文件：{output_file}\")\nprint(f\"   3. 右键文件 → 分享 → 获取链接 → 任何人可查看\")\nprint(f\"   4. 复制分享链接即可在线访问！\")\nprint(f\"\\n🌐 或者部署到 GitHub Pages / Netlify 获得永久链接\")\n","path":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/generate_online_html.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773365915173}}
