{"type":"message","id":"d0ba9892","parentId":"8ba3629f","timestamp":"2026-03-13T01:42:24.200Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"本地服务器启动了，但哥哥需要的是在线链接。让我写个脚本帮他准备 GitHub Pages 一键部署，这是最可行的自动化方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哥哥，我启动了本地服务器，但你在线访问需要**公网链接**。让我帮你准备 GitHub Pages 一键部署脚本：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3c3ae3f1122b4ed589023632","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n\n# B 站评论图片报告 - GitHub Pages 一键部署脚本\n\necho \"🚀 开始部署到 GitHub Pages...\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 检查 git 是否安装\nif ! command -v git &> /dev/null; then\n    echo \"❌ Git 未安装，请先安装 Git\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# 进入目录\ncd \"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/bili_images\" || exit 1\n\n# 检查是否已有 git 仓库\nif [ ! -d \".git\" ]; then\n    echo \"📦 初始化 Git 仓库...\"\n    git init\nfi\n\n# 添加文件\necho \"📄 添加文件...\"\ngit add \"B 站评论图片报告 - 在线版.html\"\ngit add \"B 站评论图片报告.html\" 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 提交\necho \"💾 提交更改...\"\ngit commit -m \"B 站评论图片报告 - $(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S)\"\n\n# 获取 GitHub 用户名\necho \"\"\necho \"🔗 请提供你的 GitHub 仓库地址：\"\necho \"   格式：https://github.com/你的用户名/仓库名.git\"\necho \"\"\nread -p \"输入仓库地址：\" REPO_URL\n\nif [ -z \"$REPO_URL\" ]; then\n    echo \"❌ 未输入仓库地址\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# 关联远程仓库\necho \"🔗 关联远程仓库...\"\ngit remote add origin \"$REPO_URL\" 2>/dev/null || git remote set-url origin \"$REPO_URL\"\n\n# 推送\necho \"📤 推送到 GitHub...\"\ngit branch -M main\ngit push -u origin main\n\necho \"\"\necho \"✅ 部署完成！\"\necho \"\"\necho \"📋 下一步操作：\"\necho \"1️⃣ 打开 GitHub 仓库页面\"\necho \"2️⃣ 进入 Settings → Pages\"\necho \"3️⃣ Source 选择 'main' 分支 → Save\"\necho \"4️⃣ 等待 1-2 分钟后访问生成的链接\"\necho \"\"\necho \"🌐 访问地址格式：\"\necho \"   https://你的用户名.github.io/仓库名/B 站评论图片报告 - 在线版.html\"\necho \"\"\n","path":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/deploy-to-github.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"inp