{"type":"message","id":"241a1561","parentId":"8b4434e4","timestamp":"2026-03-13T02:08:40.474Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户反馈了两个问题：1）图片裂开看不到（可能是 B 站图片防盗链问题，需要设置 Referer）；2）想要直接显示图片而不是按钮。我需要修改 HTML 代码，直接用<img>标签显示图片，并且可能需要处理图片加载问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了哥哥！两个问题我一起解决 🏹\n\n**问题 1**：图片裂开是因为 B 站图片有防盗链，需要设置 Referer  \n**问题 2**：直接显示图片，去掉按钮\n\n让我重新生成 HTML：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a82a3291aad74a608b1d031c","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nB 站评论图片 - 生成在线版 HTML 报告（修复图片显示 + 直接展示）\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport time\n\n# 配置\nBV_ID = \"BV15QAUzXEtP\"\nOUTPUT_DIR = \"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/bili_images\"\n\n# 评论数据\ncomments = [\n    {\"user\": \"鲍比烤迪克\", \"comment\": \"有没有大佬帮忙翻译翻译是因为啥 [笑哭]\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/e307257281cc97cb9a43ce67b209e23a603268895.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"队友脚下火\", \"comment\": \"之前可以正常玩，昨天突然出现这样的报错\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/3da0984bb0a1744a77510231bbe215e4518548367.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"參悟自由的意義\", \"comment\": \"嘗試，還是這樣\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/d63b678c314176e678d6fb6c8a18156814110469.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"起语风\", \"comment\": \"有没有大佬知道这个怎么解决\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/8dbd37793a7a714ab1a3d3abcd7798d9358323258.png\"},\n    {\"user\": \"赤瞳的夜刃\", \"comment\": \"这又是什么问题报错，在线等很急\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/54bfa81769c32f2591c9a86177e4067a302272043.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"阿拉斯苒\", \"comment\": \"这个是什么情况\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/73c2c27e1c9737325ca53a19af83d0e314681573.jpg\"},\n    {\"user\": \"Mad-Monk\", \"comment\": \"按照 up 的指南从头到尾试了一遍，依然如此，游戏时长 50 分钟，满满的解密环节，可能跟我用的是网吧的电脑\", \"url\": \"https://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/new_dyn/e73288fb9697e7f6e8d863b8fc33931b554905270.png\"},\n]\n\n# 生成 HTML\nhtml = f\"\"\"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>B 站评论图片抓取 - {BV_ID}</title>\n    <style>\n        * {{ margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }}\n        body {{\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Segoe UI\", Roboto, \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            min-height: 100vh;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }}\n        .container {{ max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }}\n        h1 {{\n            text-align: center;\n            color: white;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }}\n        .subtitle {{\n            text-align: center;\n            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }}\n        .card {{\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }}\n        .card:hover {{\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }}\n        .card-header {{\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 25px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }}\n        .user-name {{ font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: 600; }}\n        .comment-index {{\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\n            padding: 5px 15px;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }}\n        .card-body {{ padding: 25px; }}\n        .comment-text {{\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;\n        }}\n        .image-container {{ \n            text-align: center; \n            margin: 20px 0;\n        }}\n        .image-container img {{\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n            cursor: zoom-in;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n            display: block;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }}\n        .image-container img:hover {{ \n            transform: scale(1.02);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);\n        }}\n        .image-info {{\n            margin-top: 10px;\n            color: #666;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            text-align: center;\n        }}\n        .footer {{\n            text-align: center;\n            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            padding: 20px;\n        }}\n        .stats {{\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }}\n        .stat-item {{\n            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }}\n        .stat-number {{ font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; color: white; }}\n        .stat-label {{ color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 0.9em; }}\n        \n        /* 图片加载失败时的样式 */\n        .image-container img[src=\"\"] {{\n            display: none;\n        }}\n        .image-error {{\n            background: #fff3cd;\n            border: 2px dashed #ffc107;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #856404;\n            margin: 20px 0;\n        }}\n        .image-error a {{\n            color: #007bff;\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }}\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>📸 B 站评论图片抓取</h1>\n        <p class=\"subtitle\">BV 号：{BV_ID} | 生化危机 9 Crash 崩溃报错</p>\n        \n        <div class=\"stats\">\n            <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                <div class=\"stat-number\">{len(comments)}</div>\n                <div class=\"stat-label\">条评论</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                <div class=\"stat-number\">{len(comments)}</div>\n                <div class=\"stat-label\">张图片</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                <div class=\"stat-number\">100%</div>\n                <div class=\"stat-label\">原图画质</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\"\"\"\n\nfor i, c in enumerate(comments, 1):\n    html += f\"\"\"\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <div class=\"card-header\">\n                <span class=\"user-name\">@{c[\"user\"]}</span>\n                <span class=\"comment-index\">评论 #{i}</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card-body\">\n                <div class=\"comment-text\">\n                    {c[\"comment\"]}\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"image-container\">\n                    <img src=\"{c[\"url\"]}\" \n                         alt=\"{c[\"user\"]} 的评论图片\" \n                         referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"\n                         loading=\"lazy\"\n                         onerror=\"this.onerror=null; this.parentElement.innerHTML='<div class=\\\\'image-error\\\\'>⚠️ 图片加载失败<br><a href=\\\\'{c[\\\"url\\\"]}\\\\' target=\\\\'_blank\\\\'>🔗 点击这里查看原图</a></div>';\"\n                         onclick=\"window.open('{c[\"url\"]}', '_blank')\">\n                    <div class=\"image-info\">\n                        📸 @{c[\"user\"]} 的评论图片 | 🔍 点击图片查看原图\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\"\"\"\n\nhtml += f\"\"\"\n        <div class=\"footer\">\n            <p>🏹 小猎 · 信息捕手 | 生成时间：{time.strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")}</p>\n            <p>💡 点击图片可以全屏查看原图</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <script>\n        // 自动重试加载失败的图片\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {{\n            const images = document.querySelectorAll('.image-container img');\n            images.forEach(img => {{\n                img.addEventListener('error', function() {{\n                    console.log('图片加载失败:', this.src);\n                }});\n            }});\n        }});\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n\"\"\"\n\n# 保存 HTML\noutput_file = os.path.join(OUTPUT_DIR, \"index.html\")\nwith open(output_file, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n    f.write(html)\n\nprint(f\"✅ 已生成：{output_file}\")\nprint(f\"\\n🔧 修复内容：\")\nprint(f\"   1. 添加 referrerpolicy='no-referrer' 解决防盗链\")\nprint(f\"   2. 直接显示图片，去掉按钮\")\nprint(f\"   3. 点击图片查看原图\")\nprint(f\"   4. 加载失败时显示提示\")\nprint(f\"\\n🌐 GitHub Pages 链接：\")\nprint(f\"   https://zoopools.github.io/bili-comments/\")\n","path":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter/fix_html.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773367631552}}
